name: "Home Decorators Granite Top Kitchen Island Cart"
description: Expand your kitchen workspace and add functionality with the Granite Top Kitchen Island Cart from Home Decorators Collection. Featuring solid pine construction with a natural finish and brushed nickel hardware, this cart has an elegant granite surface for a decorative touch. With a slide-out wire basket, 1 fixed shelf, 4-bottle wine rack and spacious pullout drawer, other features include heavy-duty casters for mobility that lock in place for added safety. Ideal for your kitchen or for a patio bar, this cart will provide years of use and enjoyment.Pine constructed with natural finishBrushed nickel hardwareBrushed nickel hardwareFeatures slide-out wire storage basket, 4-bottle wine rack, 1 fixed shelf, spacious pullout drawer
